'''974體育場'''（{{Lang-ar|استاد راس أبو عبود }}）是一座為於[[卡達|卡達]][[杜哈|杜哈]]{{le|拉斯阿布阿布德|Ras Abu Aboud}}的體育場，將成為[[2022年國際足協世界盃|2022年國際足協世界盃]]比賽場館之一。

== 历史 ==
卡塔尔申办2022年世界杯足球赛时，拟建造的12座体育场中包含一座完全模块式的多哈港体育场。这座设想中的体育场建在一座人工岛上，可容纳44,950名观众，球场将在世界杯结束后完全拆卸，座椅运往发展中国家。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.hinews.cn/news/system/2010/12/13/011662870.shtml |title=揭秘2022世界杯12大体育场:总投资570亿(图) |via=南海网 |date=2010-12-13 |work=新浪 |accessdate=2020-11-29 |archive-date=2020-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205082102/http://www.hinews.cn/news/system/2010/12/13/011662870.shtml }}</ref>而实际上，卡塔尔并未采用这个设计方案<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://stadiumdb.com/designs/qat/doha_port_stadium |title=Design: Doha Port Stadium |work=StadiumDB.com |accessdate=2020-12-01 |language=en |archive-date=2020-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204172831/http://stadiumdb.com/designs/qat/doha_port_stadium |dead-url=no }}</ref>。申办成功后，卡塔尔修改了体育场建设计划，12座体育场减为8座<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://gulfnews.com/sport/football/qatar-cuts-2022-world-cup-stadia-from-12-to-eight-1.1322179 |title=Qatar cuts 2022 World Cup stadia from 12 to eight |date=2014-04-21 |work=Gulfnews |accessdate=2020-12-01 |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112021102/https://gulfnews.com/sport/football/qatar-cuts-2022-world-cup-stadia-from-12-to-eight-1.1322179 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年12月2日，在卡塔尔赢得世界杯主办权五周年纪念日当天，卡塔尔确认2022年世界杯第七座球场将选址在多哈的拉斯阿布阿布德<ref name="Qatar announces ">{{Cite news |url=https://www.qatar2022.qa/en/news/qatar-announces-location-of-seventh-proposed-venue-for-2022 |title=Qatar announces location of seventh proposed venue for 2022 |date=2015-12-02 |work=Qatar 2022 FIFA World Cup Supreme Committee |accessdate=2020-11-29 |language=en |archive-date=2020-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208174411/https://www.qatar2022.qa/en/news/qatar-announces-location-of-seventh-proposed-venue-for-2022 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，位置邻近多哈港<ref name="green-legacy" />。2017年11月26日，卡塔尔正式发布了拉斯阿布阿布德体育场的设计方案。<ref name="sports.sina-dark-science">{{Cite news |url=http://sports.sina.com.cn/g/pl/2017-11-27/doc-ifypathz6290295.shtml |title=黑科技！卡塔尔世界杯新场馆 用完可拆卸再利用 |date=2017-11-27 |work=新浪体育 |accessdate=2020-11-29 |archive-date=2017-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171130130555/http://sports.sina.com.cn/g/pl/2017-11-27/doc-ifypathz6290295.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>拉斯阿布阿布德体育场位于多哈港附近<ref name="green-legacy" />，可容纳4万名观众，并采用完全模块化设计，世界杯后可完全拆掉再利用。<ref name="new_design_first_ever">{{Cite news |url=http://stadiumdb.com/news/2017/11/new_design_first_ever_fully_demountable_stadium |title=New design: First ever fully demountable stadium |date=2017-11-27 |work=StadiumDB.com |accessdate=2020-11-29 |language=en |archive-date=2020-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701040422/http://stadiumdb.com/news/2017/11/new_design_first_ever_fully_demountable_stadium |dead-url=no }}</ref>

拉斯阿布阿布德体育场将承办2022年世界杯足球赛小组赛至四分之一决赛的比赛。世界杯后，体育场将完全拆卸，构成体育场的各模块将用于卡塔尔国内外的体育项目。<ref name="green-legacy">{{Cite news |url=https://www.fifa.com/worldcup/news/the-green-legacy-of-ras-abu-aboud-stadium |title=The green legacy of Ras Abu Aboud Stadium |date=2020-05-10 |work=FIFA.com |accessdate=2020-11-29 |language=en-GB |archive-date=2020-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211071758/https://www.fifa.com/worldcup/news/the-green-legacy-of-ras-abu-aboud-stadium |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 建筑 ==
拉斯阿布阿布德体育场采用模块式设计<ref name="home" />，主要由949个海运集装箱和模块化的钢框架组成，呼应了多哈悠久的航海传统，并与体育场所在的多哈港相协调。<ref name="green-legacy" /><ref name="design" />模块式设计有助于节省资金、节省原料、缩短工期以及减少垃圾废料。<ref name="sustainability">{{Cite web |url=https://www.qatar2022.qa/en/stadiums/ras-abu-aboud-stadium/sustainability |title=Ras Abu Aboud Stadium Sustainability |publisher=Supreme Committee for Delivery & Legacy |accessdate=2020-11-29 |language=en |archive-date=2021-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107084110/https://www.qatar2022.qa/en/stadiums/ras-abu-aboud-stadium/sustainability |dead-url=no }}</ref>体育场平面为圆角矩形，世界杯期间可容纳4万名观众。<ref name="design">{{Cite web |url=https://www.qatar2022.qa/en/stadiums/ras-abu-aboud-stadium/design |title=Ras Abu Aboud Stadium Design |publisher=Supreme Committee for Delivery & Legacy |accessdate=2020-11-29 |language=en |archive-date=2021-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118202812/https://www.qatar2022.qa/en/stadiums/ras-abu-aboud-stadium/design |dead-url=no }}</ref>体育场为芬威克·伊里瓦伦公司所设计。<ref name="goal-plans-revealed">{{Cite news |url=https://www.goal.com/en/news/plans-revealed-for-ground-breaking-2022-world-cup-stadium-in/mc4w4x0xdaaz1anrw4za01p0m |title=2022 World Cup: Plans revealed for incredible ground-breaking stadium in Qatar |date=2017-11-26 |work=Goal.com |accessdate=2020-11-29 |language=en |archive-date=2020-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208220739/https://www.goal.com/en/news/plans-revealed-for-ground-breaking-2022-world-cup-stadium-in/mc4w4x0xdaaz1anrw4za01p0m |dead-url=no }}</ref>

建成后，拉斯阿布阿布德体育场将成为世界杯历史上首座可以完全拆卸再利用的体育场。世界杯后，体育场将被拆卸，原址将改为海滨休闲场地。<ref name="home">{{Cite web |url=https://www.qatar2022.qa/en/stadiums/ras-abu-aboud-stadium |title=Ras Abu Aboud Stadium |publisher=Supreme Committee for Delivery & Legacy |accessdate=2020-11-29 |language=en |archive-date=2019-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190731184156/https://sc.qa/en/stadiums/ras-abu-aboud-stadium |dead-url=no }}</ref>

